main event: An unidentified object with flashing lights was observed near Barstow, California on September 14, 1967.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 15 minutes,The observer did not see the object but only observed the flashing lights,The object was characterized as having a spherical type light that would go off and on,No noise was associated with the sightings,Military agencies were contacted to verify the observation but found no distressed or missing aircraft.
sighted object: flashing lights from an unidentified object
